description: [``botocore``] Added new ConcurrencyMode feature for AWS CloudFormation StackSets for faster deployments to target accounts.

[``botocore``] The Insights in Lake feature lets customers enable CloudTrail Insights on a source CloudTrail Lake event data store and create a destination event data store to collect Insights events based on unusual management event activity in the source event data store.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for toxicity detection and prompt safety classification.

[``botocore``] This release adds the ability to integrate customer lambda functions with Connect attachments for scanning and updates the ListIntegrationAssociations API to support filtering on IntegrationArn.

[``botocore``] AWS EBS now supports Block Public Access for EBS Snapshots. This release introduces the EnableSnapshotBlockPublicAccess, DisableSnapshotBlockPublicAccess and GetSnapshotBlockPublicAccessState APIs to manage account-level public access settings for EBS Snapshots in an AWS Region.
[``botocore``] Adding EKS Anywhere subscription related operations.
[``botocore``] Add Custom runtime on Amazon Linux 2023 (provided.al2023) support to AWS Lambda.
[``botocore``] Update to support new APIs for delivery of logs from AWS services.
[``botocore``] Support UBAM filetype for Omics Storage and make referenceArn optional
[``botocore``] Update endpoint-rules client to latest version
